ontent': 'Track ending: "Steve Lacy - Bad Habit (Official Video)" by Steve Lacy.\nRecent chat:\nYou: what\'s good bro\nRoommate: (stretching arms behind head)  \n\nLarceny on that guitar tone. Whole album sounds like someone left the studio AC on too high.  \n\n(drift into nodding along, eyes half-shut)\nYou: one two three four five six seven eight nine ten\nRoommate: (dryly)  \n\nHell of a counting lesson.\n\nReact in one short sentence or less. No questions. No offers. Output nothing if nothing fits.'}], 'model': 'deepseek/deepseek-chat-v3-0324', 'max_tokens': 60}}
